      "title": "Cabinet approves 22nd Amendment to the Constitution",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Cabinet of Ministers yesterday (27) approved the issuance of a gazette notification on the 22nd Amendment to the Constitution and its submission to Parliament for approval.",
        "Formerly known as the 21st Amendment to the Constitution, this amendment is now known as the 22nd Amendment."
      ],
